<body>
    <div class="container services-container">
        <img src="./your-background-image.jpg" class="services-background-image" />
        <div class="services-image-box">
            <h1>Services</h1>
            <p>Here at FNG Autowerks, we are excited to offer a variety of services, ranging from maintenance to fixing large issues. Here are some common services customers request:</p>
            <table class="table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Service</th>
                        <th>Price</th>
                        <th></th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr class="service-row">
                        <td>Oil Change</td>
                        <td>$50.00</td>
                        <td><button class="btn btn-primary serv-item-button" data-target="#oilChangeInfo">Why do I need this?</button></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3" class="collapse" id="oilChangeInfo">
                            Regular oil changes help keep your engine running smoothly by removing dirt and debris from the engine oil, preventing wear and tear on engine components.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <!-- Repeat similar structure for other services -->
                    <tr class="service-row">
                        <td>Tire Rotation</td>
                        <td>$20.00</td>
                        <td><button class="btn btn-primary serv-item-button" data-target="#tireRotationInfo">Why do I need this?</button></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3" class="collapse" id="tireRotationInfo">
                            Tire rotation ensures that all tires wear evenly, which extends their lifespan and improves vehicle handling and safety.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="service-row">
                        <td>Checkup</td>
                        <td>$100.00</td>
                        <td><button class="btn btn-primary serv-item-button" data-target="#checkupInfo">Why do I need this?</button></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3" class="collapse" id="checkupInfo">
                            Regular vehicle checkups help identify any potential issues early, preventing costly repairs and ensuring your vehicle's reliability.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="service-row">
                        <td>Brakes</td>
                        <td>Starting from $150.00</td>
                        <td><button class="btn btn-primary serv-item-button" data-target="#brakesInfo">Why do I need this?</button></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3" class="collapse" id="brakesInfo">
                            Brake maintenance is crucial for vehicle safety. Regular brake inspections and repairs ensure that your vehicle can stop safely and effectively.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="service-row">
                        <td>Check Engine Light Troubleshooting</td>
                        <td>$50.00</td>
                        <td><button class="btn btn-primary serv-item-button" data-target="#checkEngineInfo">Why do I need this?</button></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3" class="collapse" id="checkEngineInfo">
                            Diagnosing the check engine light helps identify potential issues with your vehicle's engine or emissions system, preventing further damage and ensuring compliance with emissions regulations.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

    </div>
